title: Maruti's total sales rise 15% to 1,97,471 units in Feb
description: In February, Maruti Suzuki India reported a 15% year-on-year increase in total wholesales, reaching 1,97,471 units compared to 1,72,321 units in the same month last year. Domestic passenger vehicle sales grew by 9% to 1,60,271 units from 1,47,467 units last year.
